{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Atlas (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <i><b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_(shipentine)\" title=\"Atlas (shipentine)\">Atlas</a></b></i> <i>(pictured)</i> was the last of her kind to be built in the United States, and later became a canning company's flagship?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_(shipentine)","retrieved":1782896310923},{"title":"Jacob Huesman (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacob_Huesman\" title=\"Jacob Huesman\">Jacob Huesman</a></b> joined the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_Giants\" title=\"New York Giants\">New York Giants</a> as a fullback despite never having played the position before?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacob_Huesman","retrieved":1782896310936},{"title":"January 1926 Liechtenstein general election (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a candidate in the <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/January_1926_Liechtenstein_general_election\" title=\"January 1926 Liechtenstein general election\">January<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">&nbsp;</span>1926 Liechtenstein general election</a></b> was reported to the police for allegedly supporting republican views?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/January_1926_Liechtenstein_general_election","retrieved":1782896310937},{"title":"North Fork Snoqualmie River (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a proposed dam on the <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Fork_Snoqualmie_River\" title=\"North Fork Snoqualmie River\">North Fork Snoqualmie River</a></b> may have been an attempt to gain political leverage over Seattle?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Fork_Snoqualmie_River","retrieved":1782896310937},{"title":"Ceciwa Khonje (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that exiled <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ceciwa_Khonje\" title=\"Ceciwa Khonje\">Ceciwa Khonje</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\"><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">'</span>s</span> role in achieving Malawi's independence was \"rubbed out of history\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ceciwa_Khonje","retrieved":1782896310939},{"title":"Lebanon uses 15 different legal frameworks and religious courts (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_status_law_in_Lebanon\" title=\"Personal status law in Lebanon\">Lebanon uses 15 different legal frameworks and religious courts</a></b> to represent the country's 18 officially recognized sects, as opposed to a common or unified civil personal status law?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_status_law_in_Lebanon","retrieved":1782896310939},{"title":"S. Sudjojono (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Indonesian painter <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S._Sudjojono\" title=\"S. Sudjojono\">S.<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">&nbsp;</span>Sudjojono</a></b> left the Communist Party of Indonesia after it deemed him to be too immoral?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S._Sudjojono","retrieved":1782896310940},{"title":"incineration of more than 516,000 cans of soup (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the US government contracted for the <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1971_Bon_Vivant_botulism_incident\" title=\"1971 Bon Vivant botulism incident\">incineration of more than 516,000 cans of soup</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1971_Bon_Vivant_botulism_incident","retrieved":1782896310945},{"title":"was saved by a whale's tail (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that an overshooting train in Rotterdam <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rotterdam_metro_crash\" title=\"Rotterdam metro crash\">was saved by a whale's